How to install:
[/u][/b][/size][list]
[*]NMM: load it up and let the installer do the work
[*]Manual: Place The chosen preset in Skyrim>Data>SKSE>Plugins>CharGen>Presets
             Place the Head sculpt files in Skyrim>Data>SKSE>Plugins>CharGenThe ENB used in the screenshots is [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/22056/?]Reallike Enb[/url][/list]
